dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. From: Corso geografico universelle. In Venetia : In Spese dell'autore, 1691-1692. Prime meridian: Ferro. Historic Maps copy is first state as described by Burden, with "Antarctico" engraved inside double line representing the arctic circle; corrected in second state to "Arctico."
